name: Infinite Yield
description:
A powerful admin suite for Roblox games

Features:
- Keybinds that can be binded to ANY key
- Ability to set waypoints
- Plugins to allow you to create and share your own commands
- Undetected on most games
- Ability to set command aliases
- Chat and whisper logs
- Freecam
- Built-in ESP / chams / Xray
- Minimal UI
- Ability to set commands to run when you spawn
- 110+ built-in commands
author: Edge, ZWolf, Moon
